column2: SELECT m.id as [id], str (m.ra, #, #) AS ra, str (m.dec, #, #) AS dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN (sp.type) as photo_type, str (sp.modelMag_r, #, #) as r, str (sp.modelMagErr_r, #, #) as err_r, str (sp.modelMag_i, #, #) as i, str (sp.modelMagErr_i, #, #) as err_i, sp.plate, sp.mjd, sp.fiberid, str (sp.z, #, #) as spec_z, ss.snMedian_i, pp.absMagR, pp.z into MyDB.XRG_rev_check_out from MyDB.XRG_rev_check AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestSpecObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecPhoto AS sp ON n.objID = sp.objID LEFT OUTER JOIN photoZ AS pp ON pp.objID = sp.objID LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObjAll As ss ON ss.specobjID = sp.specobjID ORDER by m.id
